  <lyrics>[V1]
 Alajjpach marcajja
 Waquichatásquiwa,
 Khespitanacatac
 Cristomp jacañatac.
 
[C]
 Diosan marcapana
 Asqui jakenacaw
 Wiñay cusisipjjan
 Criston thiyapana. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Alajjpach marcaru
 Mantañataquejja,
 Khespitáñasawa
 Criston wilapampi.
 
[V3]
 Munata jilata,
 Jan juchar cutí'asa
 Cristor arcañáni
 Alajjpach marcaru.
 
</lyrics></song>